## [1.0.3] - 2023-01-22

### Added

- Added a bash_macros_edit() command to open macros.sh in Vim and then reload.

## [1.0.2] - 2023-01-13

### Fixed

- Fixed bug in bash_macros_add() that failed to add commands that had numbers `[0-9]`.
- Fixed bug in bash_macros_move() that failed to move commands that had equals `[=]`.

## [1.0.1] - 2023-01-07

### Fixed

- Fixed bug in bash_macros_add() when adding from history that included history number in command.

## [1.0.0] - 2023-01-07

### Added

- Initial release.

